      "bookSlug": "leviticus",
      "chapterNumber": 18,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Leviticus 18:25",
      "text": "וַתִּטְמָ֣א הָאָ֔רֶץ וָאֶפְקֹ֥ד עֲוֺנָ֖הּ עָלֶ֑יהָ וַתָּקִ֥א הָאָ֖רֶץ אֶת ־ יֹשְׁבֶֽיהָ ׃",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "wlc:leviticus.18.26",
